.B \-\-jsonp
Permits \fIJSONP\fP access via an HTTP interface. Enabling the
interface can increase network exposure. The \fI\%\-\-jsonp\fP option enables the
HTTP interface, even if the \fBHTTP interface\fP
option is disabled.
.UNINDENT
